#: ../../content/applications/marketing/email_marketing.rst:221
msgid ""
"The options are: :guilabel:`My Mailings`, :guilabel:`Sent Date`, "
":guilabel:`A/B Tests`, :guilabel:`A/B Tests to review`, "
