#: ../../content/applications/marketing/surveys/analysis.rst-1
msgid ""
"The 'See Results' button present on the main dashboard of the Odoo Surveys "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Butonul „Vedeți rezultatele” prezent pe tabloul de bord principal al "
